commit.message: Added new user card and accounts to those cards
Fixed spaces and tabs in dashboard
Cleanup and refactor with peewee started
Updated analytics and started using google charts there
Created the basis of the analysis page
Created the first version of the history page
Added team component and level tracking
Created view components for all the separate pages
Created view components for all the separate pages
Updated styling for top level pages
Separated out the navigation component and modified router

Initial commit for the frontend of the application.

The commited files are created with vue-cli 3 and by adding
vuetify to the project. Vuex and vue-router will also be
utilized in the project.
